                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I took the prisoners. William said he found the brushes down in the kitchen, and he kept them because his mistress had stopped is. a week of his wages.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MISS WAKELING</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I stopped his wages for three weeks, because he was late; but it was last month, not previous to Dec.</p>
